---
import PublicLayout from '@layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout title="VIP Access Activado - KicksPremium">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-brand-black text-white flex items-center justify-center py-20">
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-4 uppercase">
        ¡Bienvenido al <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-amber-500">VIP Club</span>!
      </h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg mb-8">
        Tu suscripción VIP se ha activado correctamente. Ya puedes disfrutar de todos los beneficios exclusivos.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-brand-gray border border-yellow-500/30 p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-2">Tu código de descuento VIP:</p>
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 font-display">VIP15</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-2">15% de descuento en todas tus compras</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/productos" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-amber-600 text-black px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:from-yellow-400 hover:to-amber-500 transition-all">
          Explorar Productos
        </a>
        <a href="/mi-cuenta" class="border-2 border-neutral-700 text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:border-yellow-500 hover:text-yellow-500 transition-all">
          Mi Cuenta
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
